race.description: Dad And Dave Turf Showcase Handicap
race.comment: BIG SHOT LEGEND (12) bounced straight back to form this morning with a solid chasing third at Gilgandra. Peaking now fourth-up and gets in well with the claim again. Bold showing anticipated. HALLE BEE (13) was poised to strike when resuming last time but just lacked a fitness edge late. Better for the hitout and will appreciate the rise in trip. Can give this a big shake. SILENT SERENADE (7) didn't give her rivals a sniff last start at Walcha when leading pillar-to-post. Will have to use that early dash again to overcome the wide draw and will take plenty of catching if left alone. ARRABBIATA (5) is knocking on the door and should be peaking fourth-up, though will need some luck from the car park draw.
